title: HP MSA 2040: System Health Status
agents: linux
catalog: hw/storagehw/hp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the system name and health status of a HP MSA 2040 storage system.
 If the health status is "OK" then the service will be OK.
 Otherwise the service state change to WARN or CRIT and reports a health reason.

item:
 Name of the system

discovery:
 One service is created.
